org.eclipse.scada.ds

Class DataNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.scada.ds.DataNode

  • public class DataNode
extends java.lang.Object
    A data node used for storing data in a DataStore.

    Data nodes are equal by id.

    Since:
    0.15.0

        java.io.InputStream stream)
         throws java.io.IOException
        Create a new data node and fill with the input stream

        The stream is not closed by the constructor.
